\tab\bullet\tab user deletion\par
\tab\bullet\tab notification settings updates\par
\tab\bullet\tab test notification activity\par
\tab\bullet\tab scheduled contract notification sends\par
\par
This supports accountability, troubleshooting, and post-event review.\par
\par
\b 5.7 Notification De-Duplication\b0\par
\par
The scheduled notification process currently prevents duplicate logs for the same:\par
\par
\tab\bullet\tab contract\par
\tab\bullet\tab trigger day\par
\tab\bullet\tab notification type\par
\tab\bullet\tab recipient\par
\par
This reduces repeat-message noise caused by repeated scheduled execution.\par
\par
\b 5.8 Contract Data Integrity Alignment\b0\par
\par
The frontend and backend currently align on important contract fields including:\par
\par
\tab\bullet\tab start date\par
\tab\bullet\tab review date\par
